    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/1af07d8e82066aba1af836b59efec3d6.poster.avif?t=1762853134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/1af07d8e82066aba1af836b59efec3d6.webm?t=1762853134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/1af07d8e82066aba1af836b59efec3d6.mp4?t=1762853134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>Sneak In</strong>是一个有趣的、具有挑战性和令人上瘾的大理石射击游戏。阻止邪恶和贪婪的蛇Seth吃掉所有你心爱的大理石，慢慢地潜入奇卡瓦的奇妙丛林中。赛斯，这个无畏的爬行动物，在那里生活了很久，也想收集珍贵的弹珠。通过触发<strong>连锁反应和三个弹珠的组合</strong>来阻止他，并通过超过<strong>200个独特、多彩和具有挑战性的关卡</strong>来达到记分牌上的最高位置。在<strong>无尽模式</strong>中挑战你的朋友，打败他们的高分。Sneak In是一个<strong>最令人上瘾的弹珠游戏</strong>，你会玩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/5bbf90c42bbbf88a81461be9af538436.poster.avif?t=1762853134\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/5bbf90c42bbbf88a81461be9af538436.webm?t=1762853134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/5bbf90c42bbbf88a81461be9af538436.mp4?t=1762853134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>你是否有能力阻止最凶恶的蛇Seth并在Chicahua的丛林中生存？  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/e34e8ad28a0c097780062d92956fd22c.poster.avif?t=1762853134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/e34e8ad28a0c097780062d92956fd22c.webm?t=1762853134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061550/extras/e34e8ad28a0c097780062d92956fd22c.mp4?t=1762853134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>突出特点</strong></h2>✪ 7个神奇的弹珠： 冰冻的、凹凸不平的、幽灵的、岩石的、气泡的、病毒的和黑洞的。<br>✪ 每周都有1个新的无尽模式<br>✪ 超过200个独特的挑战性关卡<br>✪ 易于学习，难以掌握<br>✪ 在多个设备上玩，云端保存<br><br>潜入奇卡瓦丛林，打败偷偷摸摸的蛇塞思，在无尽游戏模式中挑战你的朋友。还在这里吗! 在塞思吃掉你所有的美味弹珠之前，赶快行动吧!",
